# 1. Overview

This document describes the current-state (AS-IS) and future-state (TO-BE) business process flows for dealership lead management. The objective is to identify inefficiencies in the existing process and define an optimized workflow using Salesforce Automotive Cloud.

---

# 2. AS-IS Process Flow (Current State)

## Process: Lead Management

```text
Customer Inquiry
        │
        ▼
Lead Received Through Multiple Channels
(Website / Phone / Walk-In / Social Media)
        │
        ▼
Sales Manager Reviews Lead
        │
        ▼
Manual Lead Assignment
        │
        ▼
Sales Representative Contacts Customer
        │
        ▼
Follow-Up Activities Managed Manually
        │
        ▼
Test Drive Scheduling Through Calls/Emails
        │
        ▼
Customer Purchase Decision
        │
        ▼
Vehicle Sale
```

### Current Process Issues

* Manual lead assignment causes delays.
* Duplicate customer records exist.
* No lead prioritization mechanism.
* Follow-ups are inconsistent.
* Customer communication history is fragmented.
* Reporting requires manual effort.
* Sales managers lack real-time visibility.

