### Process Flow

```text
Qualified Lead
        │
        ▼
Select Vehicle
        │
        ▼
Check Availability
        │
        ├──────── Vehicle Unavailable ─────► Suggest Alternative Vehicle
        │
       Available
        │
        ▼
Select Date & Time
        │
        ▼
Create Appointment
        │
        ▼
Send Confirmation Notification
        │
        ▼
Update Appointment Calendar
```

### Output

Confirmed Test Drive Appointment

